Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to offer 43 Market Road, Sunshine, for lease.

Access to this tightly held industrial pocket of Sunshine is usually the privilege of the lucky few however 43 Market Road bucks the trend with offering all of the suburb's best delights for a fraction of the entry price.

Positioned only 700m* from Somerville Road, 2km* from Princes Freeway, 3km* from the Western Ring Road, 6km* from the Port of Melbourne and 9km* from the CBD.

This is an offering like no other.

Features include:
+ Building area: 290sqm*
+ Air-conditioned office and warehouse
+ Container height roller door
+ Reception area
+ Ample on-site parking
+ Kitchenette & amenities

*approx.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Rare opportunity to purchase in Sunshine

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present, 24 Second Avenue, Sunshine, for sale. 

This property is centrally positioned in the Sunshine Industrial precinct. Situated only metres from Market Road, providing wider access to both Sunshine and Somerville Roads, and walking distance to Sunshine Plaza and Sunshine Train Station.

Location benefits:
+ 4km* to Geelong Road/Princes Highway
+ 6km* to Port of Melbourne
+ 8km* to Tullamarine Freeway
+ 9km* to CBD
+ 13km* to Melbourne Airport

Key property features:
+ Total building area: 810sqm* 
+ 150sqm* office
+ Clear span warehouse in good condition
+ Brick construction
+ Internal clearance of 4.3m – 5.8m 
+ Fully fitted offices in good condition
+ Heating/cooling in offices
+ Male and female amenities
+ Second office and covered workshop area
+ 6 onsite car parks
+ Small storage yard
+ Three phase power
+ Roller shutter door

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to present, 2 Carrington Drive, Sunshine, for lease.

2 Carrington Drive offers two new warehouses with the ability to combine to make one larger facility. Located only 1km* from the Ballarat Road entrance to the Western Ring Road, and 1.5km* to Sunshine Bunnings.

Two properties of 460sqm* total building area can be combined by removing an internal panel to achieve 920sqm* of total building area.

Key features include:
+ Motorised sliding gate
+ Clear span warehouse with 6.5 metre + internal clearance
+ Bathroom & kitchenette
+ Additional kitchenette/sink in warehouse
+ Six car parks on each title
+ High quality finished warehouse, including internal fixtures/fittings, alucobond facade, landscaping
+ No owners corp fees

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BRAND NEW WAREHOUSE – METERS FROM BALLARAT ROAD
